{"tid":1544145,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB節目教「警黑合作」英文 點講才最準確?","createTime":"2019-09-05T12:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T16:40:37.000Z","uid":184679,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ee1afac58a9de8111557b34e35b0289315b88548","tid":1544145,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:38:50.000Z","msg":"「警黑合作」英文係......<br />\n<br />\n反修訂《逃犯條例》引發一連串示威遊行活動，無綫新聞被指報道有關新聞時偏頗，沒有完整呈現相關事件。不過近日資訊節目《睇新聞‧講英文》的最新一集，竟然教觀眾如何用英文來表達警方與黑社會合作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/09/20190903_PO_%E7%84%A1%E7%B7%9A%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F09%2F20190903_PO_%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B7%259A%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%259B%25AE4.jpg&h=130a2346&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/09/20190903_PO_%E7%84%A1%E7%B7%9A%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F09%2F20190903_PO_%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B7%259A%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%259B%25AE3.jpg&h=19cf2a5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n節目中，主持賴君蕊問另一名主持禇簡寧：「就近日連串嘅示威活動，有人質疑警方係咪同黑社會合作喎？」對方就會引警務處處長盧偉聰的說話，稱警方與黑社會是「completely opposite （勢不兩立）」。賴君蕊再問禇簡寧，如果警方與黑社會合作的英文應該怎樣說。禇簡寧就回應可以用「co-operate」表達，他再引用蘭桂芳集團主席盛智文的另一個講法，「警方不可能與黑社會合作（in cahoots with the triads）」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/09/20190903_PO_%E7%84%A1%E7%B7%9A%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F09%2F20190903_PO_%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B7%259A%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%259B%25AE2.jpg&h=d5652ac1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/09/20190903_PO_%E7%84%A1%E7%B7%9A%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F09%2F20190903_PO_%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B7%259A%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%259B%25AE1.jpg&h=5bea2d22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n禇簡寧解釋，「in cahoots with the triads」中指的「triads」是黑社會，「cahoots」是合作，不過並不是指普通的合作，而是指非法勾當、秘密協商及進行不法行為就是。賴君蕊隨即指，如果要以英文形容警方與黑社會，就可以用「police in cahoots with the triads」，不過她亦補充警務處處長盧偉聰已經否認這個指控。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/09/20190903_PO_%E7%84%A1%E7%B7%9A%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F09%2F20190903_PO_%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B7%259A%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%259B%25AE5.jpg&h=dfa023d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《睇新聞‧講英文》教觀眾如何用英文來表達警方與黑社會合作。節目截圖<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5019513-【kelly-online】無綫節目教「警黑合作」英文-「co-operate」都唔</code></pre>"},{"pid":"487bab3f81abe599bac47e0dabb20231a80777f1","tid":1544145,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:39:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"885b3df58b79c8b81da63ee7091f6bd10b159ce9","tid":1544145,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:39:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2acd278cc551307df8c458d3c2cf148dd9442275","tid":1544145,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:39:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fcb05750894c6136779b9caed236d33e2e32eec8","tid":1544145,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:40:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b